role_dependencies: Installs certbot on nearly any OS
role_description: An Ansible role that installs Android Studio on nearly any OS
role_description_full_overview: It also generates sites-enabled proxies using YML configurations. Easter eggs included. Nginx, stylized as NGINX, nginx or NginX, is a web server that can also be used as a reverse proxy, load balancer, mail proxy and HTTP cache. The software was created by Igor Sysoev and publicly released in 2004. Nginx is free and open-source software, released under the terms of the 2-clause BSD license.
